main event: A couple observed a moving light in the sky which resembled a large star while sitting on the beach in Healdsburg, California.
interesting points: The object was seen moving erratically at a steady speed, The sighting lasted over 2 hours, The object took over half an hour to reach the tree tops, It was noted to be faster than any airplane, The object emitted no sound.
sighted object: a light resembling a large star
witness description: a couple enjoying the evening on the beach
